        <h2>Where to start</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/docs/getting-started">Getting Started</a> — install and run your first command in minutes</li>
          <li><a href="/docs/concept/shadow-branch-pattern">Shadow Branch Pattern</a> — understand the concept behind the tool</li>
          <li><a href="/docs/concept/ai-memory-layer">Git Shadow as AI Memory Layer</a> — how git-shadow enables persistent AI cognition</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Commands reference</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/docs/commands/new-feature">new-feature</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/commands/commit">commit</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/commands/publish">publish</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/commands/finish-feature">finish-feature</a></li>
          <li><a href="/docs/commands/install-hook">install-hook</a></li>
